	     <div class="why-this-inner"> 
        	<div class="why-cho_inner">
        	<h2>Configuration Management</h2>
             <div class="why-cho_inner_subtext"><img src="images/magic-rabbit2.jpg" height=370 width=350>

Amazon Web Services is the new data center. Cloud services has leveled the playing field, allowing competition to enter the market with a low barrier to entry. As great as that is, it is only the beginning of leveraging the cloud for a scalable software driven infrastructure to run your business on. 

<br><br>

Automation is a key component of maximizing agility and resiliency. Configuration Management is a key concept for managing automation. Systems Engineers are well versed in using scripts for managing infrastructure. Configuration Management provides a reliable, secure way to centralize those efforts of automation. We like using Ansible which takes a minimalist approach to configuration management. 
<br><br>

One thing worth noting, there are CI/CD designs where using a configuration management tool is not the best choice. We can help you determine whether configuration management is right for your objectives. 

